# Commerce Domain

**Owns:** catalog, personalization, gift box, cart, checkout, orders, inventory, promotions, commerce admin.  
**Does not own:** editorial publish gates, creator bidding.

## Invariants (enforce in services)

| Invariant | Code anchor |
|---|---|
| Server recomputes money | `CheckoutService` uses `cart.totals` ‚Äî ignore client totals |
| Stock check + reserve | `InventoryService.assertAvailable` ‚Üí `reserve(tx, ‚Ä¶)` inside order `$transaction` |
| Available = onHand ‚àí reserved | Never let reserved exceed onHand implicitly |
| Fail/cancel releases hold | `release` / payment `FAILED` path in `PaymentFulfillmentService` |
| Capture commits stock | `commit` on `CAPTURED` |
| One line‚Äôs personalization | Must not mutate another line‚Äôs options |
| Coupons | No stack unless explicitly configured |
| Guest‚Üíuser cart merge | Deterministic, conflict-safe |

```typescript
// ‚ùå trust client
order.totalPaise = body.totalPaise;

// ‚úÖ server totals only (placeOrder pattern)
const totals = await this.cart.totals(cartDto.id, body.shippingMethod);
```

